      "review_text": "Have you ever wanted to play a bowling FPS? \r\nNo?\r\n\r\nwell, now you can anyway!\r\n\r\nSparedevil is the next \"pick up and play\" game you didn't know you needed. It's got bowling, powerups, clowns, cowboys, and other goofy things that make you wonder: what exact strain of weed was the dev smoking, and where can I get some? \r\n\r\nif you are also a connoisseur of 'weird games', this is for you.",
      "timestamp_created": 1771244185
    },
