      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 56,
      "review_text": "An absolute blast of fast paced, in your face, arcade style fun :)\n\nIt's carved out a very specific, simple and easy to drop into vibe that feels like I stumbled across an old arcade cabinet as a kid and keep draining my dad's pocket of coins. Love it, will definitely be playing more!!",
      "timestamp_created": 1770471172
    },
